Options: (a) 10!/3 (b) 10!/6 (c) 10!/2 (d) 10!/4 (e) 10!/5
A:
 The meeting can be held in 10! ways. The only protocol to be observed is that whenever they speak the pm should speak before the mp and the mp should speak before the mla. So, the meeting can be held in 10!/3 ways. So the answer is (a).

