 Let the total number of students be x. Then, 8% of x = 8x/100 = 4x/50 4/5 of x = 4x/5 10% of x = 10x/100 = x/10 20 students are not interested in any games. So, x - 8x/100 - 4x/5 - x/10 = 20 x = 20*1000/100 - 8*1000/100 - 4*1000/5 - 1000/10 = 2000 - 800 - 800 - 100 = 1300. So the answer is (c).

